author: jsdelfino
msg: Do not require the caller of new JSONRpcClient() to know the name of the binding used on the server side as the binding name is internal to the server side composition. For example this prevented Widget references to be created correctly, as they were not supposed to know the name of the binding on the target service.

author: jsdelfino
msg: Use the domain URI to configure the default domain controller port, instead of having it hardcoded.
